Code for Tsujita et al. (2026)

This repository contains the analysis code used in the study:

Tsujita et al. (2026), "Upper limit on HF(1-0) absorption in a dusty star-forming galaxy at z=6: Constraints on early fluorine enrichment", ApJL, in press,  arXiv:2602.12885
https://arxiv.org/abs/2602.12885

The scripts included here were used for data reduction and figure generation presented in the paper.

Note on the chemical evolution model:
Only the model results shown in the paper are included in this repository.
The original chemical evolution modeling code based on:

Kobayashi et al. (2020), ApJ, 900, 179
https://ui.adsabs.harvard.edu/abs/2020ApJ...900..179K/abstract

is not included in this repository.


If you notice any issues, bugs, or have questions regarding the implementation, please contact:
